{"view":"article","slug":"meffert-s-pocket-cube","category":"Non-WCA","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Non-WCA","title":{"en":"Meffert's Pocket Cube Tutorial (3x3 Bundled Cube)"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Meffert's Pocket Cube Tutorial (3x3 Bundled Cube)</strong></p><p><strong>麦菲特口袋魔方教程（三阶捆绑魔方）</strong></p><p>Yujian Song (宋雨键)</p><p><a id=\"_Hlk520216754\"></a></p><p><strong>Notation 符号表示</strong></p><p>U, L, R 均为顺时针转动90°，z为整体顺时针转动120°，z'为逆时针整体旋转120°.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image3.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image4.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Cubeshape复形</strong></p><p>归位三个1x2x2的捆绑块。</p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image6.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>归位1x1x2块（不考虑具体位置）。</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Case 1</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Case 2</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Case 3</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image7.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image8.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image9.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>L' R L R' </strong><em>(to case 4)</em></p></td><td><p><strong>R L' R' L </strong><em>(to case 4)</em></p></td><td><p><strong>R L' U L R' </strong><em>(to case 4)</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>调整方向使得1x1x2的捆绑块在U层，且非捆绑的三个小块在D层。</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>Case 4</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image10.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image11.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R L' U L R'\">R L' U L R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' R U' R' L\">L' R U' R' L</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>检验两个小角是否归位（不用管方向），若未归位，做</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image12.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' R U R' L z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L\">L' R U R' L z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>调整三个1x1x2捆绑棱的相对位置和三个小棱块的方向</strong></p><p>分析捆绑棱的置换情况。如果是三循环或者已复原则跳过该图；如果为一个对换，做</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image13.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R L' U' R' L z' R L' U' R' L z' L' R U2 R' L z R L' U L R'\">R L' U' R' L z' R L' U' R' L z' L' R U2 R' L z R L' U L R'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>观察三个小棱块的色向。如果有两块需要翻色（忽略单纯的三循环），做</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image14.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"z L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L R L' U' R' L z' R L' U' R' L z' L' R U2 R' L z R L' U L R'\">z L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L R L' U' R' L z' R L' U' R' L z' L' R U2 R' L z R L' U L R'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>复原小棱块和角块</strong></p><p>重复</p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' R U R' L z L' R U R' L z' R L' U L R' z R L' U L R'\">L' R U R' L z L' R U R' L z' R L' U L R' z R L' U L R'</span></p><p>使两个角块的方向正确，再重复</p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' R U R' L z L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U L R'\">L' R U R' L z L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U L R'</span></p><p>使三个小棱块复原。这两个公式效果都是三循环，但如果遇到的是反向三循环需要做两遍公式。</p><p><strong>三个1x1x2捆绑棱归位</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p>顺时针三棱换</p></td><td><p><strong>逆时针三棱换</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image16.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R L' U' R' L z' R L' U' R' L z' L' R U2 R' L z R L' U L R' z\">R L' U' R' L z' R L' U' R' L z' L' R U2 R' L z R L' U L R' z</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L\">L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L z'\">L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L z'</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R L' U' R' L z' R L' U' R' L z' L' R U2 R' L z R L' U L R'\">R L' U' R' L z' R L' U' R' L z' L' R U2 R' L z R L' U L R'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>至此，整个魔方全部复原。</p>"},"algs":["R L' U L R'","L' R U' R' L","L' R U R' L z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L","R L' U' R' L z' R L' U' R' L z' L' R U2 R' L z R L' U L R'","z L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L R L' U' R' L z' R L' U' R' L z' L' R U2 R' L z R L' U L R'","L' R U R' L z L' R U R' L z' R L' U L R' z R L' U L R'","L' R U R' L z L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U L R'","R L' U' R' L z' R L' U' R' L z' L' R U2 R' L z R L' U L R' z","L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L","L' R U L R' z L' R U L R' z R L' U2 L R' z' L' R U' R' L z'"],"thumb":"/stats/tutorial/media/meffert-s-pocket-cube/en/image1.png","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
